title: Indonesia : mobile phone internet users 2017 to 2023
yAxis: Number of mobile phone internet users in millions
summary: In general Number of mobile phone internet users in millions has stayed the same over the Year.
Number of mobile phone internet users in millions is slightly increasing from 2022 to 2023.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2022 and 2023.
Maximum Number of mobile phone internet users in millions, about 100.4 was reported at Year 2023
Minimum Number of mobile phone internet users in millions about 97.6 was reached at Year 2022
